{"tid":1325613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"石硤尾便利店驚現懷槍客","createTime":"2019-07-17T02:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T02:39:22.000Z","uid":99962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f75116ae3e205d072c0cb211590a7d2e6d06af98","tid":1325613,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T02:39:22.000Z","msg":"石硤尾南昌街223號地下7-11便利店，今早(17日)7時59分，職員報案指一名男子闖入店內，亮出類似手槍形物體指嚇，報警求助。疑人見狀拔足逃走，警方到場兜截，並無發現，經調查後該手槍疑為打火機，店舖沒有財物損失，案件列作可疑人處理，正調查事件動機。警員正翻查有關「天眼」片段追緝疑人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190717/bkn-20190717090323922-0717_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190717%2Fbkn-20190717090323922-0717_00822_001.html&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSdjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=673b660c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190717/bkn-20190717090323922-0717_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n省港奇兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}